    "en": {
      "title": "Coming from India is \u201cTonier 228\u201d.",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian Navy's Tonier-228 maritime surveillance aircraft is to be handed over to Sri Lanka today (15).",
        "The Government of India is going to supply 3 such surveillance aircraft to the Government of Sri Lanka, this being its first aircraft.",
        "Documents submitted to the Cabinet last March indicated that a team of five Indian technical officers would visit Sri Lanka after the aircraft was handed over. (R)"
      ],
